column5: Had to replace my printer so the new has a scanner and I thought I would give ya's some pictures to look at from a few years back   ...
Some real nice fish there.  Thanks for taking the time to scan em.
WOO HOO!!! BIG FISHIES....BIG FISHIES!!  Thanks...I needed that!
That OOS muskie must have been a lot of fun through the ice!!! lol
Didn't know what it was, kept tapping and stealing the minnows, after about the 4th minnow I hooked one through the tail and the ride was on, almost spooled the ultra light...
There's a certain something, about those pictures that I really like.

Great pics. Always nice to bring back the old memories. I got a scanner a few years back and over the winter I scanned all the old pics to computer. Now I get to see them more often and even better I have a digital copy of them on a disc stored at a friends place in case something ever happens here at the house. Nice way to ensure you'll always have a copy for the future.
